---
title: Lamb Meatballs & Spaghetti with Oregano Tomato Sauce & Parmesan
description: We’ve put a twist on classic spaghetti and meatballs by using flavoursome lamb mince and adding nutritious spinach to the sauce. And don’t forget to try our clever trick of stirring some of the pasta sauce through the spaghetti before serving – it gets every bite infused with flavour and stops the spaghetti from sticking.
